note right of InstructorFormModule
  Logic from instructor.js:
  - Handles instructor add/search/delete
  - Populates dropdowns
  - Validates and resets form
end note

note right of ClassFormModule
  Logic from class.js:
  - Handles class add/search/delete
  - Populates instructor/class dropdowns
  - Validates schedule and form
end note

note right of APIService
  Abstracts fetch calls to backend API endpoints for both Instructor and Class
end note

note right of UIUtils
  Handles UI feedback and dropdown population
end note

